flowchart TB
    P1([Participant 1])
    P2([Participant 2])
    PN([Participant N])
    Signal[Signaling Service<br/>WebSocket control plane<br/>join, mute, raise hand]
    SFU[SFU<br/>Selective Forwarding<br/>1 up, N-1 down]
    MCU[MCU<br/>Mixing Conference Unit<br/>composes single stream]
    Recordings[(Recordings<br/>object store)]

    P1 <-->|signaling| Signal
    P2 <-->|signaling| Signal
    PN <-->|signaling| Signal
    P1 -->|WebRTC SRTP| SFU
    P2 -->|WebRTC SRTP| SFU
    PN -->|WebRTC SRTP| SFU
    SFU -->|forward streams| P1
    SFU -->|forward streams| P2
    SFU -->|forward streams| PN
    SFU -.->|webinar mode| MCU
    MCU -.-> Recordings

